name: Intensive Pmax into Tempo #2
description:
After warming up, complete two sets of Intensive Pmax work. The first set consists of 5 x 20sec efforts with a recovery period of 2 minutes in Zone 2. 



The second set consists of 8 x 15sec efforts performed throughout a tempo effort. The accelerations are shorter in the 2nd set, but the pressure kept on the pedals during the recovery period will challenge your ability to recover.
